<article id="post-329" class="post-329 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-9">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.windcraft.cn/?p=329" rel="bookmark">风音周刊 010期</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		
<p>又到了周刊时间拉，感谢大家来查阅。</p>



<p>服务器在本周举行了风音破坏王活动，在线人数破历史新高，63人！</p>



<p>空岛商店因为物价问题在修改之中，预计下周完成</p>



<p>生存服商店上架了NPC兑换券，大家可以来购买自己的NPC拉！</p>



<p>生存服在本周面临巨大的实体卡顿，tps极地的问题，希望下周可以修复改善</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/U5TXF4KDW81LGW.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-330" srcset="https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/U5TXF4KDW81LGW.jpg 800w, https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/U5TXF4KDW81LGW-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/U5TXF4KDW81LGW-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.windcraft.cn/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/U5TXF4KDW81LGW-768x768.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /></figure>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ece88e2ef078d12bd05b58c0b9f9bfc4?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ece88e2ef078d12bd05b58c0b9f9bfc4?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' /><span class="screen-reader-text">作者 </span> <a class="url fn n" href="https://www.windcraft.cn/?author=1">Chinamiao</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">发布于 </span><a href="https://www.windcraft.cn/?p=329" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2020-02-24T11:40:38+08:00">2020年2月24日</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">分类 </span><a href="https://www.windcraft.cn/?cat=9" rel="category">风音周刊</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="https://www.windcraft.cn/?p=329#respond"><span class="screen-reader-text">于风音周刊 010期</span>留下评论</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
